item.title: Project 1
item.description: Christine Bandela cmb5726 0. Introduction (4 pts) For this exploratory data analysis project I have chosen two datasets that I will use to compare and contrast betweeen Game of Thrones characters and thier infuence on baby names from 1880 to 2015. The dataset ‘GOT’contains variables about the Game of Thrones characters including their first name, male, as well as, popularity. The ’Names’ dataset contains variables including YearofBirth, Number, name and Sex.
